<h1>Blueprint test pages</h1>
    <hr>

    <p>Welcome to the Blueprint test pages. The HTML files below tests most HTML elements, and especially classes provided
      by&nbsp;Blueprint.</p>

    <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">

